               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18450818-name-595" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18450818-name-595" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18450818-name-595" type="surname" value="CARTER"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18450818-name-595" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>JAMES CARTER</persName>
                  </hi>. I am foreman to Mr. John Henry Machu, a silk manufacturer in Bunhill-row. The prisoner was in his employ as a wire-ribbon weaver—he worked on his premises piece-work, and had a good character—this tool is my master's, and these pieces of iron are such as we use, and some of these I can speak to as being my master's.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18450818-name-596" type="witnessName">
